Keywords for Craft Beer Marketing

small-scale, independent brewery

small output each year

not part of a large corporation

'craftsmanship' is key

if a craft beer company is purchased by a large-scale operative, it isn't craft anymore

uses locally sourced ingredients

produces innovative, interesting, and limited-edition brews

often, craft brewers get creative with flavours and styles

You are able to visit and take a tour of breweries quite often

You are able to meet the makers and sample the products to learn more about craft beer

add a 'tour' section for people to learn more about beer




